chat.msg: hola! que comience el juego!!
face south and take the bridge to the island west
vale, crucé al bridge y ahora estoy en una island con un tiger
¿dónde voy a continuación?

you are going to cross the island, continuing towards the west. move south of the tiger. you are going to move to the west-most point of the island. if you encounter a big rock on the island, just go around it to the south and continue to the west
de acuerdo, he evitado la rock y sigo hacia el oeste
ahora veo una gran isla con un loro en un tree. ¿y ahora qué?

yes you are going to take the bridge to that island. you are going to go north of the parrot. and then you will see an elephant after the parrot (to the west). move south in between the parrot and the elephant. once you have passed the parrot, turn towards the east until you see a rock bridge.
hecho, pasé el loro y el elefante, giré al este y ya veo un puente de rocas
¿lo cruzo?

yes, cross the rock bridge. you are going to see a frog. travel south until you are past the frog. then turn east so you move under the frog. once you pass the frog, turn back around and move west until you see a crocodile or alligator bridge.
bueno, pasé al sur del toad, giré al este, luego al oeste y ahora veo un bridge con un crocodile en él
¿esto va bien?

take the crocodile bridge. there will be a path at the end where you have to choose a north or south island. choose the north island where the elephant and parrot are. then contiue west and you will see another rock bridge to an island with a giraffe. take that bridge and travel sith under the giraffe. you will then see another bridge to the final island. that that bridge and travel across the island towards the east until you see the treasure
¡lo logré! crucé el puente del crocodile, escogí la isla norte con el elephant y el loro, luego al oeste hasta llegar al puente de rocas que me llevó a la island con la giraffe
pasé al sur debajo de la giraffe, tomé el último puente y camino al este hasta que encontré el tesoro *terminado* ¡éxito total!

chat.msg: hola, empezamos?
hello yes!
estupendo
estoy en la tienda al norte, ¿por dónde empiezo?
travel south. you will see a dog to the east of you. continue south under that dog and once you pass the dog turn towards the east.
vale, voy hacia el sur, paso al dog, y después giro al este
¿continúo recto desde aquí?

you will see a fire in front of you. travel north above the camp fire. once you pass the fire you will see some mushrooms. continue traveling east under the mushrooms towards the car. once you are back on the path above the car let me know
de acuerdo, voy al norte, paso el fire, sigo al este bajo los hongos hacia el car
ahora estoy en el camino sobre el car, ¿y ahora qué hago?

turn back around and travel west on the road until you see the path take a fork. take the path south until you see a telescore. travel south between the telescope and a bush to the west of it, diverging from the path. when you are back on the path turn towards the west. follow the path west a little until you see a circle of rocks. you will see a path of rocks leading to that circle. go northwest below the path of rocks until it merges with the circle. continue west until you hit the cabin
vale, regreso, voy al oeste hasta la bifurcación, luego sur hasta el telescope, sigo al sur entre el telescope y un arbusto al oeste, vuelvo al camino y giro al oeste hasta los rocks
voy al noroeste debajo del camino rocoso hasta llegar al círculo, continúo al oeste, llegué a la cabaña *terminado*
